type: Superalgos Review - A Great First Step

definition.text: The onboarding of the superalgos tutorial was a fun way to get started with the system.

paragraphs.text: The included tutorials make learning about superalgos easy and convenient. The guides were well written and the ability to stop and resume the tutorials is very useful. I encountered no errors in the system while using it and only one small UI hangup. Overall it was a great introduction to the system.
